<bibRefCitation author="Walker" box="[530,764,403,429]" etAl="et al." firstAuthor="Walker" pageId="162" pageNumber="163" refId="ref332116" refString="Walker, H. J. Jr., Hastings, P. A., Hyde, J. R., Lea, R. N., Snodgrass, O. E. &amp; Bellquist, K. F. (2020) Unusual occurrences of fishes in the Southern California Current System during the warm water period of 2014 - 2018. Estuarine and Coastal Shelf Science 236. https: // doi. org / 10.1016 / j. ecss. 2020.106634" type="journal volume" year="2020">
